<div>
	<h1>Rules of KBC Game</h1>
	<ul>
		<li>There will be 16 Questions in total.</li>
		<li>The Questions 5th and 10th will be the two barriers.If you cross it then you will be able to take that much of amount surely.</li>
		<li>After crossing 10th Question , the 16th Question i.e Jackpot Question will get open.</li>
		<li>You will be provided with four lifelines.</li>
			<ul>
				<li>Phone a friend</li>
				<li>50-50</li>
				<li>Flip the Question</li>
				<li>Expert Advice</li>
		</ul>
		<li>You can use one lifeline only once i.e You cannot repeat the same lifeline.</li>
		<li>Once you reaches the Jackpot Question than you will not be able to use any lifeline if it is with you.</li>
		<li>Till Question 5th you will get 45 sec per question and after that till question 10th you will get 60 sec.</li>
		<li>After Question 10th till 15th question you will get a time of 90 sec per question.</li>
		<li>Another option is Quit, you can choose anytime and your game gets stopped and you will achieve current winning amount.</li>
		<li>But if you Quit before 5th Question you will not be able to recieve any amount.</li>
	</ul>
	
